Package cip.render

The programs and classes that support 3D modelling, animation, and rendering.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDynXmlObject
    This is the interface to a dynamically loaded object described in an XML node.
    INamedObject
    This is the interface for a named object.
    IRenderScene
    This is the interface to components that render a scene.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ADynamicNamedObject  
    DynXmlObjLoader
    This is the loader for dynamically loaded objects from XML files.
    FrameLoader
    This is a frame loader for an XML description of a frame.
    MyFileFilter
    Provides the dialogue for picking a file to be written to
    RenderCanvas  
    RenderWindow
    This is the main for window-centric rendering.
    TestRenderScene
    This is a test IRenderScene implementation that simply paints a repeating horizontal red gradation overlaid with a repeating vertical blue gradation.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DynXmlObjParseException
    The exception thrown by a dynamically loaded object described in an XML file.

Package cip.render Description

The programs and classes that support 3D modelling, animation, and rendering. Ray tracing specific code is in it's own subdirectory.
